Jack Ross: "My highest aspiration is to lead Scotland"
Sunderland Technical Director Jack Ross says his "highest aspiration" is to become Scotland's manager sooner or later.
The 42-year-old is drawn to the challenge of resurrecting the Northeast team that is currently in third place in League One, three points from the top.
